dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"lm學野"},{"pid":"93ffa143b946b5a0faa9e2382c62d43203ec7dda","tid":471554,"uid":82881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有冇邊本投資嘅書比較易明同啱新手睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投資書就工具書黎架姐，除非你睇返3、5、7本，再靈活運用先有效，否則你睇得一本半本，就去實戰買股票好易比大戶舞黎舞去。不過點講都好，股票市場無天書，實戰失敗就係最好的教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651a3df3ec81cce531bbd806f912432f99b5598c","tid":471554,"uid":118010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有冇邊本投資嘅書比較易明同啱新手睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投資書就工具書黎架姐，除非你睇返3、5、7本，再靈活運用先有效，否則你睇得一本半本，就去實戰買股票好易比大戶舞黎舞去。不過點講都好，股票市場無天書，實戰失敗就係最好的教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n謝指教"},{"pid":"8fb636d8e38e9793c28ded30c00235c3f5be52da","tid":471554,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"先預一半本黎交學費"},{"pid":"3a97b04645b849d618dbc64d0eeaf58644b2a3ef","tid":471554,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"認真，買Index fund"},{"pid":"af9d222e6e890c5607256ff0b1e71274e9a09a01","tid":471554,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"可以試下睇 「不離地的股票投資哲學與實踐」 前幾日係學校書店見到<br />\n<br />\n見你戶口果D都未識開 本書印象中真係由0開始教 可能啱你<br />\n<br />\n因為我都係上兩星期先第一次開戶口買股票 當時情況同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b67d64d041eaa092c0a81e5fa649b6f876a524","tid":471554,"uid":158078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有冇邊本投資嘅書比較易明同啱新手睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投資101 <a href=\"http://同aastock.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8Caastock.com&d=l9G0vbJcOBQTwCvWYd%2BVKv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=238ce1e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">同aastock.com</a>本身都有，起碼你要明d terms點解。之後揾d基本分析書，黃國英好似有一本，唔使好叻但起碼知d financial report點睇。到呢到為止d basic野應該識得7788"},{"pid":"e8a3c3caa81ba58f02b1e01b35b93d45a315f885","tid":471554,"uid":158078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有冇邊本投資嘅書比較易明同啱新手睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投資101 同<a href=\"http://aastock.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faastock.com&d=l9G0vbJcOBQTwCvWYd%2BVKv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9a2e3eea\" target=\"_blank\">http://aastock.com</a>本身都有，起碼你要明d terms點解。之後揾d基本分析書，黃國英好似有一本，唔使好叻但起碼知d financial report點睇。到呢到為止d basic野應該識得7788</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後我會建議先玩正股，期權/輪/金就放埋一邊先，當然depends on你自己揀啦。之後就睇下唔同玩法係點，曹仁超/peter lynch/施洛德etc, 呢下就可以落場交下學費，試下自己覺得點玩先comfort"}]}